Achievements.Name: Overachiever
Achievements.Description: Attain all the Achievements! The path of the warrior demands this from those who walk on it!

Achievements.Name: Fashion Plate
Achievements.Description: Even a top rate fighter needs to coordinate properly! You gotta get all of the Colors first!

Achievements.Name: Dan the Man
Achievements.Description: Mastery of the Saikyo arts requires mastery of the Personal Action! Collect 'em all, punk!

Achievements.Name: Entitled
Achievements.Description: A Title does not tell all of a man, sir, but if I were to see one Title, I'd want them all...

Achievements.Name: Iconoclast
Achievements.Description: Oh my gosh, those Icons are so adorable! I gotta find Don-chan and catch 'em all!

Achievements.Name: Special Movement
Achievements.Description: Do a Special Move 100 times! If you're a true student of the Rindo-kan dojo, it's your duty!

Achievements.Name: EXtra! EXtra!
Achievements.Description: Battle requires courage! Train by using your EX Gauge to successfully land 100 EX Moves!

Achievements.Name: Super, Man!
Achievements.Description: To battle is to win a fight with overwhelming strength! Show me you can do 100 Super Combos!

Achievements.Name: Ultra, Man!
Achievements.Description: If yer gonna fight, give it your all, pal. Performing 100 Ultra Combos oughta do it, eh?

Achievements.Name: It Takes Focus
Achievements.Description: Your mission, should you wish to join Delta Red, is to connect with 100 Focus Attacks!

Achievements.Name: Superior Super
Achievements.Description: Trust your instincts and winning will come easy. Let's begin with 50 Super Combo finishes!

Achievements.Name: Ultimate Ultra
Achievements.Description: Candy always says you gotta win with style, so go out there and perform 50 Ultra Combo finishes!

Achievements.Name: Sunspotter
Achievements.Description: Amigo, perform 365 Super or Ultra Combo finishes against your opponents! The dawn is coming!

Achievements.Name: Absolute Perfection
Achievements.Description: Lauren's waiting, so how about you finish your fights quickly and get 30 Perfects. Sound good?

Achievements.Name: Clear Headed
Achievements.Description: Hey! Got time to kill? Try to clear Arcade Mode on Medium or higher! That's all you gotta do!

Achievements.Name: All Clear
Achievements.Description: To get strong takes lots of fighting! Clear Arcade Mode on Medium or higher with all characters!

Achievements.Name: Herculean Effort
Achievements.Description: Can you finish Arcade Mode on Medium or higher without using a continue? Show me you can!

Achievements.Name: Hard Times
Achievements.Description: To escape death is to beat the strongest of the strong. Finish Arcade Mode on Hardest, kid!

Achievements.Name: Long Time No See
Achievements.Description: Do you wish for defeat? If so, complete Arcade Mode on Hardest difficulty and beat Gouken!

Achievements.Name: Rival Schooled
Achievements.Description: See your future by clearing every Rival Battle on Medium or higher with every character.

Achievements.Name: Speed Freak
Achievements.Description: Finish each round in Arcade Mode on Medium or higher in 20 seconds or less. Too easy.

Achievements.Name: Good Start
Achievements.Description: All of nature must withstand a trial. You must clear 10 trials in Trial Mode to succeed.

Achievements.Name: Trail of Trials
Achievements.Description: There is no shortcut in the art of Yoga. Aim to clear any character's Trial Mode trials!

Achievements.Name: Trial Athlete
Achievements.Description: I shall assimilate all and be all-powerful! Clear all Trial Mode challenges, and so can you!

Achievements.Name: Oh! My Car!
Achievements.Description: Hee hee, destruction is so much fun! Score 80,000 points or more in the Car Crusher bonus stage!

Achievements.Name: Barrel of Laughs
Achievements.Description: No need for barrels without oil! Score 110,000 points or more in the Barrel Buster bonus stage!

Achievements.Name: It Begins
Achievements.Description: The fight starts here! Set your Title and Icon, and begin fighting on Xbox Live!

Achievements.Name: First Timer
Achievements.Description: I'll never forget my first time for Ryu's sake! Win one Ranked Match! Gotta aim for the top!

Achievements.Name: Threepeat
Achievements.Description: You think being this good is easy? Let's see you win 3 Ranked Matches in a row, champ!

Achievements.Name: Fivepeat
Achievements.Description: This is your real power, child? Show me it's not luck by winning 5 Ranked Matches in a row!

Achievements.Name: Tenpeat
Achievements.Description: Don't hold back your true potential! Win 10 Ranked Matches in a row!

Achievements.Name: Moving On Up
Achievements.Description: Ya need to do anything to reach the top of the food chain! Let's see a Rank Up via Ranked Match!

Achievements.Name: Now You C Me...
Achievements.Description: I wrestle only the strong! You shall rank up to C Rank if you wanna face me, comrade!

Achievements.Name: From C to Shining C
Achievements.Description: You think you're good, don't you? Prove it by ranking up all characters to C Rank!

Achievements.Name: Road to Victory
Achievements.Description: You wanna get that fight money? You're gonna have to win 10 Xbox LIVE matches first, sucka!

Achievements.Name: Battle Master
Achievements.Description: Only winners can attain such beauty. Win 30 Xbox LIVE matches and I may share my beauty secrets.

Achievements.Name: Legendary Fighter
Achievements.Description: I shall make you the right hand of Shadaloo if you can win 100 Xbox LIVE matches!

Achievements.Name: Worldly Warrior
Achievements.Description: Let's do this, amigo! Fight 50 Xbox LIVE matches, because that's the only way to become strong!

Achievements.Name: Bring it on!
Achievements.Description: No comrade, this will not do! We must become stronger, for our fans! Fight 100 Xbox LIVE matches!

Achievements.Name: This is Madness!
Achievements.Description: Fighting is fun, huh? Well then, let's aim for 300 Xbox LIVE matches fought, OK buddy?

Achievements.Name: Team Player
Achievements.Description: A 1-on-1 fight is fun, but it's more fun with friends! Try fighting in a Team Battle!

Achievements.Name: Team Mate
Achievements.Description: Win 1 Team Battle match, and you will learn that teamwork can help you become stronger!

Achievements.Name: Teamworker
Achievements.Description: A pro can win with any team. Win 10 Team Battles but don't forget, you have to win too!

Achievements.Name: Keep on Truckin'
Achievements.Description: If you want to focus on nothing but the fight, entering an Endless Battle is for you!

Achievements.Name: Three For The Road
Achievements.Description: In the pursuit of strength, one must have a goal! In Endless Battle win 3 matches in a row.

Achievements.Name: Endless Ten
Achievements.Description: Throw away your fears and focus on the fight! Win 10 fights in a row in Endless Battle!

Achievements.Name: Replayer
Achievements.Description: Watch 30 Replays via the Replay Channel! Isn't it fun watching people go at it tooth and nail!?

Achievements.Name: Endless Lobbyist
Achievements.Description: It's only natural for warriors to seek fights! Create 30 Endless Battle lobbies!

Achievements.Name: Team Lobbyist
Achievements.Description: Hey mon, battlin' is fun, no? Go out and create 30 Team Battle lobbies and enjoy the rhythm!

Achievements.Name: Quarter Up
Achievements.Description: Fight 30 opponents via Arcade Fight Request. It'd be easy with the right bait, he he.
